Text:
The Cool Kids is an alternative hip hop group from the Mid-West United States. 
The duo consists of Antoine "Mikey Rocks" Reed (originally from Matteson, Illinois) 
and Evan "Chuck Inglish" Ingersoll (originally from Mount Clemens, Michigan). 
Self-described as "the new black version of the Beastie Boys," The Cool Kids' music 
has been released primarily to the independent Chocolate Industries via their own 
label C.A.K.E. Recordings...
